channel.title: Dinging Floorboards - Tropical Original
channel.description:
Hello everyone! I hate to say this but this might be my last track for awhile. My SoundCloud minutes are out and this was the only song I could bring out. I’m buying pro unlimited in the future.
Anyways here is the song.
Soundcloud: [Dinging Floorboards-Tropical Original](https://soundcloud.com/tropical_madman/dinging-floorboards-tropical)
This wait might be a long while and I’m not sure when I will be back. So I’ll see you all soon!
Tell me what you think of the song. This is my number 1 song of the year. (Until I make a new finished song)

item.title: Dinging Floorboards - Tropical Original

item.description:
Sounds really good. Mad skills.
Btw it could be more catchy if you start with the leading bass earlier.

Nevertheless you do a very very good job. Go ahead!
